{
  "stem": "8212.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Definitely with strangers.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that two years after, they shipped her out to Theresienstadt.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It's just incredible to me what she went through.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think it's part of the city.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think so.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it's mostly Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It affected me and my sister in a way that we went through so many-- after Vienna, we went through so many situations where we were in camps and make-do situations-- that we always had a-- an incredible yearning for beautiful things and beautiful surroundings, both of us.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And whether it's clothes, silverware, a plate, a little vase-- we always looked for flowers, for the beautiful things in life.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "For art.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "For-- it was very important to us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Music, things like that, spiritual things.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Very much.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we were terribly striving for that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I was trying to bring up my children in this direction.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm always trying to do things for people, whenever I can.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "To be part of it, to help.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "About six years ago, I had cancer.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I had ovarian cancer, and I was very lucky to pull through.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I must say, I had a pretty good attitude.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I believed that I would be well again, and I am.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I am very lucky.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But I always try to help people who have that same experience.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Even yesterday somebody called me-- tell them what happened, because people are so afraid of just the word, cancer; of the word, chemotherapy.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You lose your hair.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It's a terrible thing for a woman to lose her hair.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I did.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I mean, it just came out in bushels.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It was a horrible thing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "At the end, I didn't even dare comb my hair anymore.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It was just a matted mess.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
